snippet.title: Aquaman’s Amber Heard reveals how she realized Mera is a woman superhero done right
snippet.description:
Al Arabiya's William Mullally speaks with Aquaman star Amber Heard about her friendship with Jason Momoa, how she discovered that Mera was a woman superhero who wasn't another one-dimensional stereotype, and whether she's interested in a sequel.
